    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the plan I've laid out:\n\n## Plan: `uv cache stats`\n\n**7 files** to touch (2 new, 5 modified). No new dependencies needed — `diskus` and all other pieces are already in use.\n\n### What the command will produce\n\n```\nwheels        1.2 MiB      # or raw bytes without --human\nsdists        384.0 KiB\nflat-index    12.0 KiB\ngit           0B\ninterpreter   4.0 KiB\nsimple        256.0 KiB\narchive       8.0 MiB\nbuilds        0B\nenvironments  25.3 MiB\npython        5.4 MiB\nbinaries      0B\nTotal         40.5 MiB\n```\n\n### Key design decisions\n\n| Decision | Rationale |\n|----------|-----------|\n| Reuse `PreviewFeature::CacheSize` gate | `cache stats` is closely related to `cache size`; no new bit needed |\n| Include `Python` bucket (missing from `CacheBucket::iter()`) | `iter()` is used for clean-by-name ops, not reporting; Python is a real on-disk bucket |\n| Total = sum of per-bucket values | Transparent and consistent with what's shown above |\n| Column width computed dynamically | \"environments\" is the longest (12 chars); avoids hardcoding |\n| `0B` not `0.0B` for zero bytes | Matches the style already used in `cache_size.rs` for the empty case |",
